Habakuk ywagore ni adiera onge


1  Ma e wach mane Ruoth Nyasaye onyiso janabi Habakuk e fweny.


2  A Ruoth Nyasaye, nyaka karang’o ma anyalo ywaknie mondo ikonywa, to ok iwinja? Aywakni ka awacho niya, ‘Masira’, to ok ireswa. 
3  Ere gima omiyo iweyo aneno chandruok machalo kamano? Koso ang’o momiyo iweyo aneno timbe mamonogi? Mecho kod timbe machach ema aneno, kendo miero gi lweny olwora koni gi koni. 
4  Kuom mano ji ok luw chik, kendo buche ok yal gi adiera, nimar joma timbegi mono thoth, mohewo joma kare. Mano emomiyo adiera iloko aloka.

Okor wach ni jo-Babulon biro sando jo-Juda


5  

Ruoth Nyasaye ne odwoka niya, “Winjuru un joma andhokegi! Gimoro biro timore ma ubiro wuoro kendo biru bwogou, nimar abiro timo gimoro e ndalou, ma ok unuyie kinyisou. 
6  

Abiro kelo jo-Babulon, ma oganda mager kendo ma jomrima! Giwuotho e piny ngima ka gimayo jomoko nono miechgi. 
7  Gin joma ger marach, kendo gitimo mana gima gin ema gidwaro to onge ng’ama geng’ogi. 
8  Faresegi jong’wech moloyo kwach, kendo ger moloyo ondiegi mawuotho ka piny oselil. Joidh faresegi a kuma bor, kendo gihuchore mana ka ongo ma yudho gima omako, 
9  kendo joma temo geng’ogi, leny nono koneno kaka gilich. Gichoko ji ma gimako mang’eny mana ka kuoyo.


10  “Gijaro ruodhi kod jodonggi, bende giseyo kuonde mochiel motegno mag siro lweny, nikech gidhuro pidhe mag lowo, ma giidhogo ohinga, kendo gimuko kuonde mochiel motegnogo. 
11  Bang’e gikadho piyopiyo mana ka yamo, ka gidhi kamoro machielo. To kata kamano gin joketho nikech gikwano tekregi giwegi ka nyasachgi.”

Habakuk ywagore ni Ruoth Nyasaye


12  A Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasacha kendo ma Ng’ama Ler, donge in e Nyasaye ma nyaka nene kendo mochwere? A Ruoth Nyasaye ma Lwandawa, in ema iketo jo-Babulon mondo okumwa king’adonwa bura. 
13  In to iler ma ok inyal yie neno richo, kata yie nenoo timbe mamono. Koro ere gima omiyo irango aranga joma andhokegi, to ok itim gimoro? Koso ang’o momiyo iling’ aling’a ka joma richo tieko joma kare moloyogi.


14  Koro imiyo ji chalo mana gi rech ma e nam, kata gi gik malak piny, ma onge gi jotelo. 
15  Jo-Babulon mako ji mana kaka jolupo mako rech gi olowu, kendo ywayogi gi tol ka mor. 
16  Bang’e gikulore ni tondegigo kendo giwang’onigi ubani ka giwacho niya, “Magi e nyiseche ma kelonwa mwandu, momiyo wadak maber.” 
17  A Nyasaye, koro ibiro weyo gitimo kamano nyaka chieng’ ka ginego ogendini anega, to ok idew?

